Package: claude-docker
Version: VERSION_PLACEHOLDER
Architecture: all
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Maintainer: devslaweekq
Depends: curl
Description: Isolated Claude Code in Docker
  Runs Claude Code (Anthropic AI assistant) in an isolated Docker container
  with persistent sessions, TLS support, and a project workspace mount.
  .
  On install Docker is set up automatically if absent, the image is pulled
  from Docker Hub, and the launcher is added to PATH.
